<h2 id="___sec25" class="anchor">Exercise 2: Quand le prochain mouvement r&#233;trograde de la plan&#232;te Mars? </h2>

<p>
Changez la p&#233;riode et trouvez le prochain mouvement r&#233;trograde de la plan&#232;te Mars.

<p>
<!-- --- end exercise --- -->

<p>
<!-- !split -->

<h2 id="___sec26" class="anchor">Mouvement des lunes galil&#233;ennes - d&#233;but du programme  </h2>
<p>

<!-- code=python (!bc pycod) typeset with pygments style "default" -->
<div class="highlight" style="background: #f8f8f8"><pre style="line-height: 125%"><span></span><span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># IMPORTATION</span>
<span style="color: #008000; font-weight: bold">import</span> <span style="color: #0000FF; font-weight: bold">ephem</span> <span style="color: #008000; font-weight: bold">as</span> <span style="color: #0000FF; font-weight: bold">ep</span>
<span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># NOUS CRÉONS LES OBJETS</span>
Io <span style="color: #666666">=</span> ep<span style="color: #666666">.</span>Io()
Eu <span style="color: #666666">=</span> ep<span style="color: #666666">.</span>Europa()
Ga <span style="color: #666666">=</span> ep<span style="color: #666666">.</span>Ganymede()
Ca <span style="color: #666666">=</span> ep<span style="color: #666666">.</span>Callisto()
<span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># Créons des tableaux vide pour</span>
<span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># SAUVEGARDER LES COORDONNÉES</span>
y <span style="color: #666666">=</span> []
xIo <span style="color: #666666">=</span> []
xEu <span style="color: #666666">=</span> []
xGa <span style="color: #666666">=</span> []
xCa <span style="color: #666666">=</span> []
</pre></div>
<p>
<!-- !split -->

<h2 id="___sec27" class="anchor">Mouvement des lunes galil&#233;ennes - boucle principale  </h2>
<p>

<!-- code=python (!bc pycod) typeset with pygments style "default" -->
<div class="highlight" style="background: #f8f8f8"><pre style="line-height: 125%"><span></span><span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># pas de temps - heure</span>
dt <span style="color: #666666">=</span> ep<span style="color: #666666">.</span>hour
<span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># temps initial</span>
ts <span style="color: #666666">=</span> ep<span style="color: #666666">.</span>now()
<span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># heure actuelle</span>
tm <span style="color: #666666">=</span> ts
N<span style="color: #666666">=2*24</span>
<span style="color: #008000; font-weight: bold">for</span> i <span style="color: #AA22FF; font-weight: bold">in</span> <span style="color: #008000">range</span>(N):
    <span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># nous calculons des valeurs y</span>
    y<span style="color: #666666">.</span>append((tm <span style="color: #666666">-</span> ts)<span style="color: #666666">*24.0</span>)
    <span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># nous calculons des valeurs x</span>
    Io<span style="color: #666666">.</span>compute(tm)
    Eu<span style="color: #666666">.</span>compute(tm)
    Ga<span style="color: #666666">.</span>compute(tm)
    Ca<span style="color: #666666">.</span>compute(tm)
    <span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># nous ajoutons des calculs aux tableaux</span>
    xIo<span style="color: #666666">.</span>append(Io<span style="color: #666666">.</span>x)
    xEu<span style="color: #666666">.</span>append(Eu<span style="color: #666666">.</span>x)
    xGa<span style="color: #666666">.</span>append(Ga<span style="color: #666666">.</span>x)
    xCa<span style="color: #666666">.</span>append(Ca<span style="color: #666666">.</span>x)
    <span style="color: #408080; font-style: italic"># on augmente le temps d&#39;une heure</span>
    tm <span style="color: #666666">+=</span> dt
</pre></div>
<p>
<!-- !split -->

<h2 id="___sec28" class="anchor">Mouvement des lunes galil&#233;ennes - le graphique  </h2>
<p>

<!-- code=python (!bc pycod) typeset with pygments style "default" -->
<div class="highlight" style="background: #f8f8f8"><pre style="line-height: 125%"><span></span><span style="color: #008000; font-weight: bold">from</span> <span style="color: #0000FF; font-weight: bold">pylab</span> <span style="color: #008000; font-weight: bold">import</span> <span style="color: #666666">*</span>
fig1 <span style="color: #666666">=</span> plt<span style="color: #666666">.</span>figure()
plot(xIo, y, marker <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;o&quot;</span>, label <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;Io&quot;</span>)
plot(xEu, y, marker <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;o&quot;</span>, label <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;Europa&quot;</span>)
plot(xGa, y, marker <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;o&quot;</span>, label <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;Ganimedes&quot;</span>)
plot(xCa, y, marker <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;o&quot;</span>, label <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;Callisto&quot;</span>)
plot(zeros(<span style="color: #008000">len</span>(y)),y ,marker <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">r&quot;$\mathcircled{J}$&quot;</span>, markersize <span style="color: #666666">=15</span>,
     label <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;Jupiter&quot;</span>,color <span style="color: #666666">=</span><span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;orange&quot;</span>, fillstyle<span style="color: #666666">=</span> <span style="color: #BA2121">&#39;none&#39;</span>)
xlabel(<span style="color: #BA2121">u&quot;position par rapport à Jupiter&quot;</span>)
ylabel(<span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;Heures à partir de (</span><span style="color: #BB6688; font-weight: bold">%s</span><span style="color: #BA2121"> TU)&quot;</span><span style="color: #666666">%</span> ts)
ylim(<span style="color: #666666">0</span>,N<span style="color: #666666">+3</span>)
title(<span style="color: #BA2121">u&quot;Mouvement des lunes galiléennes&quot;</span>)
grid()
legend(loc <span style="color: #666666">=1</span>)

tight_layout()
savefig(<span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;../figs/mvtjov.pdf&quot;</span>); savefig(<span style="color: #BA2121">&quot;../figs/mvtjov.png&quot;</span>)
show()
</pre></div>
